3+1D Ideal Hydro 

--> Initial condition from optical Glauber and Monte Carlo Glauber model .
--> HLLE algo to solve hydro equation
--> Freezeout hypersurface will be generated in "hydro_output/" folder in .xml format.
    One can use that .xml file as input for therminator code. 


Note : Some classes in this code are inspired from the reference below.

